  <brief_title>Study of the Effects of Probiotics Upon Infectious Episodes in Subject Aged More Than 60, During Winter.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Daily Consumption of a Probiotic on the Evolution of Infectious Episodes (ENT, Gastro-intestinal and Pulmonary), in Subject Aged 60 Years or Over, During Winter.</official_title>
