  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We put forward that probiotics have an effect on infectious episodes evolution in subjects
      aged 60 years or over. The main objective of this research is to observe the effect of
      consumption of the probiotic on the average number of days with infectious episodes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
